[Episode 23]

4
00:01:42,990 --> 00:01:44,300
I've recorded the time required and fuel consumption

5
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,520
of each way-point.

6
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:51,400
Why didn't you record

7
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,690
the wind speed and direction at each altitude level?

8
00:01:53,690 --> 00:01:55,080
It doesn't matter.

9
00:02:18,970 --> 00:02:19,940
Let me show you.

10
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,920
This time, Luzhou Airlines

11
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:25,840
prepared food, clothes, masks,

12
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:28,110
cotton blankets, tents, boots,

13
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,579
medicine, medical equipment, and so on.

14
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:32,320
There are 857 pieces in total.

15
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,840
It weighs 52 tons altogether.

16
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,280
The cargo bay of 787

17
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,540
and part of the cabin have been filled up.

18
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,840
These used to be the seats of the cabin.

19
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,680
They were all removed

20
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:43,120
to store our supplies.

21
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,840
Also, we have 30 volunteers

22
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,880
from all departments at Luzhou Airlines.

23
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:51,210
Say hello to the camera.

24
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,240
Shout out our slogan.

25
00:02:54,390 --> 00:02:55,630
Mount Lan, fighting!

26
00:02:55,829 --> 00:02:57,270
Mount Lan, fighting!

27
00:03:21,930 --> 00:03:22,930
Count carefully.

28
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,320
Yicheng.

29
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,520
What are you writing?

30
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,100
Let me show you the map.

31
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,560
This is our destination.

32
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,500
We'll pass through a mountain trail.

33
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,120
Let me do it.

34
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,650
But it's hard to go this way.

35
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,610
We might need to pay attention.

36
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:36,520
Yu.

37
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:37,800
Zhang.

38
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,160
Distribute the walkie-talkie to the heads of departments.

39
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,240
Call me if you need anything.

40
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:41,900
Okay.

41
00:03:43,010 --> 00:03:44,720
The supplies have arrived in Guizhou.

42
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:46,400
We are now busy

43
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,440
with the last preparation.

44
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:50,220
The most troublesome thing is

45
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:51,230
the stock counts.

46
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:52,850
It's all here, right?

47
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,010
Where is the progress now?

48
00:03:55,010 --> 00:03:55,680
It'll be loaded soon.

49
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,540
Our supplies will be loaded soon.

50
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,930
We will split into two teams and deliver the supplies

51
00:03:59,930 --> 00:04:01,810
to the designated location in these two days.

52
00:04:01,810 --> 00:04:02,340
OK.

53
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:05,260
This is Captain Gu.

54
00:04:05,810 --> 00:04:06,210
Hello.

55
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:06,920
Hello.

56
00:04:07,510 --> 00:04:08,520
Thank you very much.

57
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,120
By the way,

58
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:10,730
the disaster situation at Wangjiaping and Shidong Village

59
00:04:10,730 --> 00:04:11,970
are still very serious.

60
00:04:11,970 --> 00:04:14,000
Some of the power and communication has been cut off.

61
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,180
The Cangshui Elementary School that you supported

62
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:17,370
is in Wangjiaping.

63
00:04:17,660 --> 00:04:18,839
If we go there now,

64
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:20,470
it'll be very difficult.

65
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,400
The more difficult it is, the more helpful it is.

66
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,120
Don't worry.

67
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,440
We will make a plan in advance

68
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,700
and deliver the supplies.

69
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:27,550
That's great. Thank you, captain.

70
00:04:27,550 --> 00:04:28,660
Also, we have arranged for

71
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:30,800
accommodation at the countryside for you.

72
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,680
But the condition

73
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,200
is definitely not as good as in the city.

74
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,480
Please understand that.

75
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,409
You're too kind.

76
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,800
We're here to work.

77
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,590
Thank you so much.

78
00:04:38,590 --> 00:04:39,320
Get in the car.

79
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,530
-You go first.
-Okay.

80
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,480
Thank you.

81
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:09,390
[Lanshan County]

82
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:09,390
[Shancheng Guesthouse]

83
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:32,730
Why are you dazing here alone?

84
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:35,670
I just discussed this with Ms. Ai.

85
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:37,670
34 people are divided into 5 groups.

86
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:39,180
We went to Wangjiaping.

87
00:06:53,260 --> 00:06:56,060
I knew something was wrong with you when in the car.

88
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,380
What are you thinking?

89
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:08,110
When I came here,

90
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:10,560
I suddenly remembered

91
00:07:11,810 --> 00:07:13,210
the night in my hometown.

92
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,130
It was the same as here.

93
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:17,890
There are no lights

94
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:20,110
but the stars in the sky.

95
00:07:24,610 --> 00:07:25,410
This place

96
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:27,390
will recover soon

97
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,900
and become calm as before.

98
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:33,460
But the disappointment in the victims' hearts...

99
00:07:34,409 --> 00:07:34,930
Tell me.

100
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:38,370
How long will it take to clean it up?

101
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,110
One year in middle school,

102
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:51,110
there was a flood.

103
00:07:53,890 --> 00:07:55,550
Our family crawled to the roof

104
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,220
waiting for help.

105
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:01,540
Sometimes,

106
00:08:01,570 --> 00:08:03,700
we saw animals' carcasses drift away.

107
00:08:04,350 --> 00:08:05,280
Some were people

108
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,980
we didn't know if they were dead or alive.

109
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:13,880
You never talked

110
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:15,860
about this.

111
00:08:19,170 --> 00:08:19,900
At that time,

112
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:23,620
my parents borrowed money to open a store.

113
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:25,960
They wanted to save more money

114
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:28,020
for my brother and me to go to college.

115
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,260
But

116
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,059
the store was washed away.

117
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:37,320
Back then, I couldn't even afford the school expenses.

118
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,400
My textbooks

119
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:40,590
were donated by others.

120
00:08:41,460 --> 00:08:42,179
The donors

121
00:08:43,110 --> 00:08:44,510
were kids from big cities

122
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:46,040
like you.

123
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,980
At that time, I thought

124
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:59,100
I must get into a good university.

125
00:09:00,010 --> 00:09:01,070
I must leave there.

126
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,890
I want to change my fate.

127
00:09:26,890 --> 00:09:28,090
You two are in the mood

128
00:09:28,430 --> 00:09:29,820
to spend time here.

129
00:09:32,570 --> 00:09:33,790
After leaving the company,

130
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:35,690
Song has become bolder.

131
00:09:36,490 --> 00:09:37,820
I found something good.

132
00:09:37,930 --> 00:09:39,550
It's a local specialty, romantic baked tofu.

133
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:40,070
Try it.

134
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:43,260
It has an auspicious implied meaning. We should try it.

135
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:44,460
I wonder

136
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,740
if my Nanting loves it.

137
00:09:46,290 --> 00:09:47,350
Don't joke around.

138
00:09:48,540 --> 00:09:49,670
What is this called?

139
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,080
Romantic baked tofu.

140
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:13,170
What do you think?

141
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,280
Not bad.

142
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,690
It does taste like romance.

143
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:36,830
Does it taste sweet?

144
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,820
I heard the road to Wangjiaping is hard to pass.

145
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:19,840
I left two pickup trucks.

146
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,170
The gas tanks are ready.

147
00:11:21,220 --> 00:11:23,550
I'm sure it'll go back and forth smoothly.

148
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:24,240
Cheng Xiao,

149
00:11:24,930 --> 00:11:25,790
drive this car.

150
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:27,650
The car's condition is better.

151
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:29,070
How can you let a girl drive?

152
00:11:29,070 --> 00:11:29,800
Let me drive.

153
00:11:30,570 --> 00:11:30,970
Let me.

154
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,280
I'm good at transporting goods.

155
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,410
Besides, Brother Zhan,

156
00:11:34,410 --> 00:11:35,690
you stayed up all night

157
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,920
and didn't rest well.

158
00:11:36,950 --> 00:11:38,550
You can take a rest in the car.

159
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:39,880
You're so considerate.

160
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:40,820
Okay.

161
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,480
I'll take your car.

162
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,480
We can take turns if you're tired halfway.

163
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,140
No problem.

164
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:47,190
The signal here is bad in most places.

165
00:11:47,190 --> 00:11:49,440
Call me with the radio in the car if anything happens.

166
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,510
I studied the route last night.

167
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:51,720
Remember to follow tight my car.

168
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,310
Okay.

169
00:11:52,590 --> 00:11:53,790
Okay, let's go.

170
00:11:55,650 --> 00:11:57,020
Brother Nanting, let me help you with the GPS.

171
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:57,980
I'll go with you.

172
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,290
You can take Xiao's car.

173
00:12:05,090 --> 00:12:06,350
None of your business.

174
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:18,200
The car is full. Take this.

175
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,590
Okay.

176
00:12:34,570 --> 00:12:37,570
Brother Nanting, we're going into the mountain area.

177
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,840
We are about to wind up the mountain.

178
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,800
It's a rough road.

179
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:43,530
Be careful. Follow me closely.

180
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:45,880
Don't worry. I won't hold you back.

181
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,120
Why is this tune so familiar?

182
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:07,980
Isn't this the one you listened

183
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,910
when you took my car the first time?

184
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,710
Yes, that's it.

185
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:15,860
The front is going to be bumpy.

186
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:17,380
I play a piece of music for you

187
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:18,440
to get the feeling.

188
00:13:50,950 --> 00:13:53,260
[Cangshui Elementary School]

189
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:15,430
I guess no one is here.

190
00:14:17,590 --> 00:14:20,610
This is Cangshui Elementary School, sponsored by Luzhou Airlines.

191
00:14:20,610 --> 00:14:21,950
Fortunately, the terrain here is high.

192
00:14:21,950 --> 00:14:23,900
It's not completely corroded by the flood.

193
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:25,020
But I can still see

194
00:14:25,050 --> 00:14:26,510
the mark left by the flood.

195
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,680
Someone's here.

196
00:14:40,830 --> 00:14:41,280
Hello.

197
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,210
Hello.

198
00:14:43,350 --> 00:14:44,980
We're volunteers from Luzhou Airlines.

199
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:46,780
We're here to deliver supplies.

200
00:14:47,310 --> 00:14:48,510
Thank you. Thank you.

201
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:50,400
Come and sit inside.

202
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:51,600
Come in.

203
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,470
Take care.

204
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,080
Thank you.

205
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,200
Ms. Guo,

206
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:07,880
hasn't the class been suspended?

207
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:09,660
Why are they still at school?

208
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:12,490
Their parents work in other places.

209
00:15:12,490 --> 00:15:14,220
They haven't come back for years.

210
00:15:14,220 --> 00:15:15,150
Due to the flood,

211
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:17,480
the electricity is off and there's no signal.

212
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,470
Their houses were soaked in water.

213
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:21,430
So I brought them to stay at school.

214
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:24,100
What about

215
00:15:24,770 --> 00:15:25,500
your family?

216
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,680
He works in Shenzhen.

217
00:15:29,350 --> 00:15:30,510
But recently,

218
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:32,940
I haven't been able to contact him for days.

219
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:35,660
How are the kids?

220
00:15:37,310 --> 00:15:38,110
They're fine,

221
00:15:38,430 --> 00:15:39,420
just hungry.

222
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,660
The food prepared by the village

223
00:15:41,660 --> 00:15:42,850
is almost finished.

224
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:45,440
I planned to go back to the village for supplies tomorrow,

225
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,610
but you came.

226
00:15:47,090 --> 00:15:48,950
You wanted to walk back and get it.

227
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:50,680
It takes half an hour to drive

228
00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:52,080
from here to the village.

229
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,680
How long does it take to walk?

230
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:56,520
Besides, you're still in this health condition.

231
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:59,090
I have no choice.

232
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,470
The children are growing.

233
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:01,870
We can't let them starve.

234
00:16:04,110 --> 00:16:05,870
How long has your pregnancy been?

235
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:06,580
Six months.

236
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,590
Is the kid sick?

237
00:16:13,730 --> 00:16:15,830
The temperature here varies greatly between day and night. It's also humid.

238
00:16:15,830 --> 00:16:17,160
Maybe she caught a cold.

239
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:35,320
Listen to me.

240
00:16:35,740 --> 00:16:37,200
Drink this cold medicine.

241
00:16:37,870 --> 00:16:38,740
Then,

242
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:42,260
I'll reward you a candy.

243
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:45,390
So that you won't feel bitter eating medicine.

244
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:45,920
Okay?

245
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:01,970
Besides leaving enough supplies,

246
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:02,570
how about

247
00:17:03,020 --> 00:17:04,220
we stay here tonight?

248
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:06,609
Ms. Guo is alone.

249
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,900
She is not convenient.

250
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:09,700
What if something happens?

251
00:17:11,589 --> 00:17:12,069
Okay.

252
00:17:13,020 --> 00:17:13,880
How about this?

253
00:17:13,900 --> 00:17:14,770
You can contact the county rescue command centre

254
00:17:14,770 --> 00:17:16,460
through the car radio

255
00:17:17,010 --> 00:17:18,869
and tell them about our schedule.

256
00:17:19,619 --> 00:17:20,390
Then ask them

257
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:21,680
to send two volunteers

258
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:22,430
to take over.

259
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,010
Okay, that's it.

260
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,849
Let's send the supplies to Wangjiaping first.

261
00:17:25,849 --> 00:17:26,440
Hurry back.

262
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:26,770
Okay.

263
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,800
Do we have enough groundsheets?

264
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,310
Yes.

265
00:17:46,990 --> 00:17:49,130
♫I always want to say goodbye♫

266
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:52,730
♫To yesterday♫

267
00:17:54,150 --> 00:17:58,910
♫I want to forget all those unpleasant moments♫

268
00:18:01,810 --> 00:18:03,920
♫I always hope to see you♫

269
00:18:05,580 --> 00:18:07,400
♫And tomorrow♫

270
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:13,130
♫I want to escape from the origin of a trivial dilemma♫

271
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:12,830
Wait for me. I want to go too.

272
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:13,810
Sit here.

273
00:18:16,100 --> 00:18:22,850
♫I have to wear a smile too even covered in mud♫

274
00:18:23,380 --> 00:18:29,990
♫I don't want the fragile side to be seen♫

275
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:37,350
♫I look up at the beginning of the shining light♫

276
00:18:38,300 --> 00:18:44,370
♫Can't wait to start a new transformation♫

277
00:18:44,690 --> 00:18:47,020
♫Like a shining star♫

278
00:18:48,410 --> 00:18:51,870
♫Just cross this over♫

279
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:58,700
♫Travel beautifully between the thorns♫

280
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:55,650
Nanting.

281
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:56,700
Got it.

282
00:18:59,350 --> 00:19:02,020
♫Like a shining star♫

283
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:01,840
Hello.

284
00:19:02,220 --> 00:19:03,360
Is this the disaster relief command centre?

285
00:19:03,260 --> 00:19:06,790
♫Just cross this over♫

286
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:05,580
We're volunteers from Luzhou Airlines.

287
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:06,820
How can I help you?

