00:33:31,890 --> 00:33:33,950
she left Dou to me and never came back.

579
00:33:36,190 --> 00:33:36,700
Later,

580
00:33:38,340 --> 00:33:40,200
my mom could take care of my child.

581
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:42,570
But she

582
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,340
is sick and in poor health.

583
00:33:46,890 --> 00:33:47,440
So,

584
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:51,560
I can only take care of my daughter alone.

585
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,750
If you

586
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,210
need any help in the future,

587
00:34:00,250 --> 00:34:01,180
just let me know.

588
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:03,490
Me too.

589
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:05,900
Count me in.

590
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:09,340
OK.

591
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:12,159
Thank you, everyone. Thank you.

592
00:34:28,850 --> 00:34:29,360
Okay.

593
00:34:30,370 --> 00:34:30,880
Are you done?

594
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:31,670
Let it go and try it.

595
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:32,320
I'm going to let it go.

596
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,159
Let it go.

597
00:34:34,659 --> 00:34:35,190
OK?

598
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,960
Okay.

599
00:34:38,560 --> 00:34:39,080
Alright.

600
00:34:39,080 --> 00:34:39,940
When the kids come back,

601
00:34:39,940 --> 00:34:41,670
they can have classes as usual.

602
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:42,330
How is it?

603
00:34:44,219 --> 00:34:45,320
Try the basketball hoop.

604
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:45,790
Try it.

605
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:47,730
My hand is injured.

606
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:48,960
I'm with Mr. Gu.

607
00:34:50,080 --> 00:34:50,880
My legs aren't working either.

608
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,610
I'm also with Brother Nanting.

609
00:34:52,949 --> 00:34:53,880
What do you mean?

610
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:55,560
You underestimate me.

611
00:34:56,170 --> 00:34:57,530
Okay, one on three.

612
00:34:58,790 --> 00:34:59,350
Come on.

613
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:09,130
Xia Zhi.

614
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:13,920
Can you give me a few minutes?

615
00:35:22,330 --> 00:35:22,980
Today,

616
00:35:23,980 --> 00:35:24,980
it's too dangerous.

617
00:35:24,980 --> 00:35:26,110
Don't do this again.

618
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:30,450
I knew you were still worried about me.

619
00:35:36,990 --> 00:35:38,850
Regarding what happened before,

620
00:35:40,080 --> 00:35:40,940
no matter what,

621
00:35:42,390 --> 00:35:43,850
I have to apologize to you.

622
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:45,580
I was too angry.

623
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:48,480
I thought about it later.

624
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,290
I force you like that

625
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:52,730
is no different from my mom.

626
00:35:57,060 --> 00:35:59,060
Do you remember the day we first met?

627
00:36:00,090 --> 00:36:02,000
On a mountain road in Shangri-La,

628
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:04,540
It's very similar to here.

629
00:36:05,530 --> 00:36:07,320
You were hitching a ride on the side of the road,

630
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:08,980
but none of them answered you.

631
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:09,970
To be honest,

632
00:36:09,970 --> 00:36:11,920
I dared not let you get in my car.

633
00:36:12,210 --> 00:36:13,140
Because you were

634
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,270
with dishevelled hair and a dirty face,

635
00:36:14,270 --> 00:36:15,560
wearing a black down jacket

636
00:36:15,560 --> 00:36:16,560
like a bear.

637
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:17,790
People might think

638
00:36:17,790 --> 00:36:18,850
you came out to rob.

639
00:36:20,230 --> 00:36:21,650
Was it easy for me?

640
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:24,510
I went on a poor trip after the college entrance exam.

641
00:36:24,510 --> 00:36:26,020
I spent a month in the west.

642
00:36:26,670 --> 00:36:28,090
I only have ten yuan left.

643
00:36:28,490 --> 00:36:30,350
I hadn't taken a shower for a week.

644
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:34,600
But fate is so magical.

645
00:36:35,010 --> 00:36:36,790
My car got stuck in the ditch.

646
00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:38,950
You came and towed the car for me.

647
00:36:40,250 --> 00:36:41,490
In that situation,

648
00:36:41,520 --> 00:36:42,760
I had no choice

649
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:44,020
to let you get in my car.

650
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:47,320
Then I saw you.

651
00:36:47,550 --> 00:36:49,320
Oh my god, it was a girl.

652
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:54,130
Then we became friends.

653
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:56,400
Then I found

654
00:36:56,690 --> 00:36:58,080
this girl is so loyal.

655
00:36:58,310 --> 00:37:00,110
She's more loyal than many boys.

656
00:37:00,850 --> 00:37:02,760
Once I came back from Rio de Janeiro,

657
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:03,760
I had a high fever.

658
00:37:04,040 --> 00:37:05,630
You spent a month's living expenses

659
00:37:05,630 --> 00:37:07,430
coming from school to be with me.

660
00:37:08,640 --> 00:37:09,720
At that time, I knew

661
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:11,640
I, Cheng Xiao,

662
00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:13,500
will be your best friend forever.

663
00:37:22,790 --> 00:37:23,400
Xia Zhi.

664
00:37:24,870 --> 00:37:25,930
Can we not

665
00:37:26,220 --> 00:37:27,600
fight over

666
00:37:28,070 --> 00:37:30,070
with such a trivial matter anymore?

667
00:37:30,570 --> 00:37:31,890
I apologized to you.

668
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:34,110
Can you forgive me?

669
00:37:42,060 --> 00:37:43,290
Actually, last time,

670
00:37:44,250 --> 00:37:44,940
I was wrong.

671
00:37:46,630 --> 00:37:47,980
I didn't do my job well.

672
00:37:48,290 --> 00:37:50,350
Yet I'm still complaining about you.

673
00:37:50,530 --> 00:37:52,390
I'm afraid you'll look down on me.

674
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:56,520
How is that possible?

675
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:59,080
Ms. Ai told me

676
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:01,180
you had improved a lot at work.

677
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,450
In the publicity part,

678
00:38:02,450 --> 00:38:04,050
you got the star of the month.

679
00:38:04,570 --> 00:38:06,230
I'm more and more proud of you.

680
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:09,950
It turns out that you've been paying attention to me.

681
00:38:09,950 --> 00:38:11,520
You're such a talent with great potential,

682
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:13,120
I have to pay attention to it.

683
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:15,510
Xia Zhi.

684
00:38:16,180 --> 00:38:17,220
I sincerely hope

685
00:38:17,250 --> 00:38:18,180
you can find a job

686
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,360
that suits you.

687
00:38:24,640 --> 00:38:25,470
Let's pretend

688
00:38:25,770 --> 00:38:27,570
nothing happened before, okay?

689
00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:29,640
No.

690
00:38:31,150 --> 00:38:32,510
Don't be like this.

691
00:38:33,160 --> 00:38:34,200
They say that

692
00:38:34,200 --> 00:38:35,760
if we reconcile after a conflict,

693
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:37,160
it means we are really close.

694
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,080
That's good.

695
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,740
Fine, I won't forget.

696
00:38:39,950 --> 00:38:40,980
Come with me to get something.

697
00:38:40,980 --> 00:38:42,840
OK. Be gentle. Don't strangle me.

698
00:39:31,170 --> 00:39:32,090
Go to sleep.

699
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,480
Are you asleep?

700
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:12,560
I know you're not asleep.
